## Resource

### `AssistantEventResource`
```json
{
  "id": "...",
  "content": "Cumpleaños de Carlos",
  "event_at": "2026-05-15T00:00:00Z",
  "event_end": null,
  "type": "birthday",
  "recurrence_rule": "FREQ=YEARLY",
  "status": "active",
  "reminders": [
    { "id": "...", "fire_at": "2026-05-08T...", "message": "...", "status": "pending" }
  ]
}
```

